sections.heading: to 48-5B-14 - Repealed.
sections.text:
Repeals.— Laws 1997, ch. 83, § 1 repealed 48-5B-1 to 48-5B-3, 48-5B-5 to 48-5B-7, 48-5B-9, 48-5B-14 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1995, ch. 157, §§ 1 to 14 and by Laws 1995, ch. 56, §§ 4 and 9, and as amended by Laws 1996, ch. 56, §§ 1 to 8, relating to producer's liens, effective June 20, 1997. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1996 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.

Laws 1996, ch. 56, § 10, repealed 48-5B-4, 48-5B-8, 48-5B-10 to 48-5B-13 NMSA 1978, as enacted by Laws 1995, ch. 157, §§ 4, 8, and 10 to 13, relating to producer's liens, effective May 15, 1996. For provisions of former sections,seethe 1995 NMSA 1978 onNMOneSource.com.
